flowchart TD
    A[Start: Search, Insert, or Delete Operation]
    B[Begin at Root Node]
    A --> B

    C[Compare Key with Current Node's Keys]
    B --> C

    D{Is Key Less, Equal, or Greater?}
    C --> D

    D -->|Less| E[Move to Left Child Node]
    D -->|Equal| F["Key Found (for Search) or Update/Delete"]
    D -->|Greater| G[Move to Right Child Node]

    E --> C
    G --> C

    F --> H[Operation Complete]

    I{"Is Node Full? (for Insert)"}
    F --> I
    I -->|Yes| J[Split Node and Promote Middle Key]
    I -->|No| H

    J --> K[Rebalance Tree if Needed]
    K --> H
